[normal]Similar to Canterbury, the diocese is looking to expand its affiliation scheme, especially as more schools work in clusters. “It is something we are actively looking to develop as we feel there will be a need for it,” says Dr Lees. “As we look at how the education world is changing, we need to be ready to respond, be more flexible and expand provision where it is needed.”
